Danvers, MA, based Investment company Stonehearth Capital Management, LLC buys The Home Depot Inc, sells Exxon Mobil Corp, Verizon Communications Inc during the 3-months ended 2017-06-30, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Stonehearth Capital Management, LLC. As of 2017-06-30, Stonehearth Capital Management, LLC owns 23 stocks with a total value of $71 million.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: HD, Added Positions: BSV, AOA, PSK, AAPL, Reduced Positions: VWO, DBEF, VEA, VB, FM, IJH, SPHQ, GE, EEMV, XOM, 
